## ðŸ§© The Core DevOps Lifecycle

DevOps can be visualized as an **infinity loop**, representing continuous processes that feed into each other:

```mermaid
flowchart LR
    A[Plan] --> B[Code]
    B --> C[Build]
    C --> D[Test]
    D --> E[Release]
    E --> F[Deploy]
    F --> G[Operate]
    G --> H[Monitor]
    H --> A
